oom-six">音爆六号</a>。</p><p>现在，组织者已经分享了 Bearded Theory 2024 的完整阵容。在 100 多个新名字中，有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dexys">Dexys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/baxter-dury">Baxter Dury</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/don-letts">Don Letts</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-big-moon">The Big Moon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/therapy">Therapy?</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marika-hackman">Marika Hackman</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/goat-girl">Goat Girl</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prima-queen">Prima Queen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dry-cleaning">Dry Cleaning</a> 。</p><p>在这里查看更新后的官方阵容海报： </p><figure id="attachment_3594925" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594925" style="width: 2481px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594925" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/BeardedTheory2024-line-up-poster.jpg" alt="大胡子理论2024阵容海报" width="2481" height="2481" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/BeardedTheory2024-line-up-poster.jpg 2481w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/BeardedTheory2024-line-up-poster-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/BeardedTheory2024-line-up-poster-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/BeardedTheory2024-line-up-poster-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/BeardedTheory2024-line-up-poster-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/BeardedTheory2024-line-up-poster-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/BeardedTheory2024-line-up-poster-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2481px) 100vw, 2481px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3594925" class="wp-caption-text">大胡子理论 2024 年阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><blockquote class="instagram-media" dat